  <entry>
    <title>java数组遍历--foreach</title>
    <url>/2022/06/13/Java/Bugs/java%E6%95%B0%E7%BB%84%E9%81%8D%E5%8E%86-foreach/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h4 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h4><p>在练习数组的使用时，想用foreach循环给数组赋值，但得到了一个空数组。</p>
<span id="more"></span>
<h4 id="bug出处"><a href="#bug出处" class="headerlink" title="bug出处"></a>bug出处</h4><p>原示例代码：</p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> java.util.Random;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">Test</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title function_">main</span><span class="params">(String[] args)</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="type">Random</span> <span class="variable">random</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">Random</span>();</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="type">int</span> arr[] = <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">int</span>[<span class="number">10</span>];</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="type">String</span> <span class="variable">s</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="string">&quot;[&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="type">int</span> <span class="variable">i</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="number">0</span> ; i &lt; arr.length; i++) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            arr[i] = random.nextInt(<span class="number">889</span>-<span class="number">22</span>) + <span class="number">22</span>;<span class="comment">//[0, 889-22) + 22</span></span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        System.out.println(<span class="string">&quot;打印数组元素：&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="type">int</span> i : arr) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            s += i + <span class="string">&quot;, &quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        s = s.substring(<span class="number">0</span>, s.length()-<span class="number">2</span>) + <span class="string">&quot;]&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        System.out.println(s);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        System.out.println(<span class="string">&quot;打印数组中是3的整倍数的元素：&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        s = <span class="string">&quot;[&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="type">int</span> i : arr) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> (i % <span class="number">3</span> == <span class="number">0</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                s += i + <span class="string">&quot;, &quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        s = s.substring(<span class="number">0</span>, s.length()-<span class="number">2</span>) + <span class="string">&quot;]&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        System.out.println(s);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>此段代码给数组元素赋值时，使用foreach循环，赋值失败。<br>通过后续查资料想进一步完善其用法，发现foreach循环<strong>不是完全的不能改变原有数组的值</strong>。</p>
<h4 id="四种情况"><a href="#四种情况" class="headerlink" title="四种情况"></a>四种情况</h4><p>首先foreach的格式如下：</p>
<blockquote>
<p>For (类型 变量名:集合) { 语句块; }</p>
</blockquote>
<p>此处的 <em><strong>类型 变量名</strong></em> 指的是使用第三方变量<strong>复制了</strong>迭代指向的数据。这里我简单的理解为一个temp。</p>
<h5 id="基本数据类型数组（int）"><a href="#基本数据类型数组（int）" class="headerlink" title="基本数据类型数组（int）"></a>基本数据类型数组（int）</h5><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span>[] list1 = <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">int</span>[<span class="number">10</span>];</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 迭代，循环依次指向数组中元素，用第三方变量i记录</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 没有对原有数据作出改变</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="type">int</span> i : list1) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    i = <span class="number">10</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">System.out.println(Arrays.toString(list1));</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>与原有的例子一样，此处遍历得到的结果如下：<br><img src="/img%5Cjava%E6%95%B0%E7%BB%84%E9%81%8D%E5%8E%86-foreach%5C1.jpg"></p>
<p>既然foreach只是用第三方变量记录，记录基本数据类型不存在赋值过程，自然不会对原数组作出改变。如此，记录引用数据类型，记录的是地址，照理说应该能对原数组作出改变了。</p>
<h5 id="引用数据类型数组（String）"><a href="#引用数据类型数组（String）" class="headerlink" title="引用数据类型数组（String）"></a>引用数据类型数组（String）</h5><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">List&lt;String&gt; list2 = <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">ArrayList</span>&lt;&gt;();</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="type">int</span> <span class="variable">i</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="number">0</span>; i &lt; <span class="number">10</span>; i++) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    list2.add(<span class="string">&quot;s&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 迭代，循环依次指向数组中元素，用第三方变量s记录</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 引用数据类型，改变原有地址值中的数据</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> (String s : list2) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    s = <span class="string">&quot;l&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">System.out.println(list2.toString());</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>此处遍历得到的结果如下：<br><img src="/img%5Cjava%E6%95%B0%E7%BB%84%E9%81%8D%E5%8E%86-foreach%5C2.jpg"></p>
<p>对原数组依然没有作出改变，理由是String被final修饰，s &#x3D; “l”只是在内存中new了一个对象，使String指向新的对象，但是此处s为第三变量，第三变量的引用改变，对于原list中记录的值不会有任何改变。既然如此，记录了地址的二维数组，没有被final修饰，应该就可以改变第二层循环内的的数据了。</p>
<h5 id="引用数据类型-（二维数组（int-））"><a href="#引用数据类型-（二维数组（int-））" class="headerlink" title="引用数据类型 （二维数组（int[][]））"></a>引用数据类型 （二维数组（int[][]））</h5><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span>[] a1 = &#123;<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">3</span>&#125;;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span>[] a2 = &#123;<span class="number">4</span>, <span class="number">5</span>, <span class="number">6</span>&#125;;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span>[] a3 = &#123;<span class="number">7</span>, <span class="number">8</span>, <span class="number">9</span>&#125;;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span>[][] arr = &#123;a1, a2, a3&#125;;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 迭代，循环依次指向数组中元素，用第三方变量s记录</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 引用数据类型，改变原有地址值中的数据</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// arr没有被final修饰，此处就是在源地址处改变，改变成功</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="type">int</span>[] ints : arr) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    ints[<span class="number">1</span>] = <span class="number">2</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="type">int</span>[] ints : arr) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    System.out.println(Arrays.toString(ints));</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>此处遍历得到的结果如下：<br><img src="/img%5Cjava%E6%95%B0%E7%BB%84%E9%81%8D%E5%8E%86-foreach%5C3.jpg"></p>
<p>可以看到第二层循环内的改变成功。如此推断，如果数组中的元素是没有被final修饰的引用数据类型，应该就是可以通过foreach改变。可以自建一个JavaBean格式的Num类测试一下。</p>
<h5 id="引用数据类型（普通类）"><a href="#引用数据类型（普通类）" class="headerlink" title="引用数据类型（普通类）"></a>引用数据类型（普通类）</h5><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">List&lt;Num&gt; list3 = <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">ArrayList</span>&lt;&gt;();</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="type">int</span> <span class="variable">i</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="number">0</span>; i &lt; <span class="number">10</span>; i++) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    list3.add(<span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">Num</span>(<span class="string">&quot;s&quot;</span>));</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 迭代，循环依次指向数组中元素，用第三方变量s记录</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 引用数据类型，记录为地址，改变原有地址值中的数据</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 改变成功</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> (Num num : list3) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    num.setNum(<span class="string">&quot;l&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">System.out.println(list3);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>此处遍历得到的结果如下：<br><img src="/img%5Cjava%E6%95%B0%E7%BB%84%E9%81%8D%E5%8E%86-foreach%5C4.jpg"></p>
<p>可以看到，改变成功。当然如果只是final修饰类，没有修饰属性，属性也是可以进行修改的。</p>
<p><strong>总结</strong>:数组中元素是引用数据类型，并且该数据类型不是jdk提供的被final修饰的数据类型（例如String, Integer…），那么就可以通过foreach修改原数组中存储的数据。<em>此处也有点像方法中的传参</em>。</p>
]]></content>
